abstract: Cisco Systems’ streak of lackluster earnings continued as the company failed to ignite its lagging business.
snippet: Cisco Systems’ streak of lackluster earnings continued as the company failed to ignite its lagging business.
lead_paragraph: Cisco Systems’ streak of lackluster earnings continued on Wednesday as the company failed to invigorate its slow-growing business.
